Editing is faster than ever! Open a project go directly to the Edit screen. Tap the Add button and import a photo to create a new scene without recording any video. Cinema Pro Pack is expanded to include Multi Layer effects Spin Blur and Spin Focus. And Tracking Blur now also blurs when a layer is rotating or zooming. Multi Layer includes multi expand in addition to mirror expand . New FREE Multi Layer distortions: Squish 2 Swirl 4 and Nightmare Now localized into Polish

3.0 Our Biggest and Boldest Update Ever! This update includes a bunch of new FREE features and some terrific new Power Packs! Video Star is the 1 music video making app in the world and in this new version we re putting the music on center stage with new effects that pulse pound and pop to the beat! Video Star analyzes your music detects beats and frequencies and uses the results in 2 new Power Packs with a total of 35 brand new music beat based effects each with several variations. There are effects that pulse and morph to the beat background effects to visualize your music and colors that cycle in time to the beat. We ve even boosted Advanced AutoStop with a brand new Beat Sync timing mode. Hear see and become a part of your music! While we were at it we also added: Mondrian Attacks! a crazy animated abstract art layout Power Pack Video Star Perks Pack a collection of must have tools onion skinning clap to record early access to free effects and more and our loyal fans who own any other Power Pack can unlock it for FREE! And since this release is all about music we ve added more ways to use your music with Video Star. Now you can work with audio podcasts and import music from other compatible apps. Finally it wouldn t be a Video Star update without FREE effects for everyone. We ve added over a half dozen new cool free effects that you are going to love. Update now!

Button is at the bottom of the lightning bolt page New in Version 1.9.5: Two AWESOME new power packs plus a new way to keep in touch with the latest Video Star freebies music videos and app news. Green Screen 3D Worlds Create stunning videos by immersing yourself in these sixteen awesome 360 degree environments. Perform in front of moving clouds and rotating landscapes. Or dance beneath the Northern Lights! Other backgrounds include a psychedelic cityscape a concert hall a cathedral an animated world map and more. Totally Hyper Titles Make your on screen text move with eight new titles styles! Now you can have text with animated sparkles or rainbow colors or text that swivels or swings down into place. And we ve added Video Star notifications sign up to be notified instantly when new music effects or featured videos are released!

Minor bug fixes and performance improvements New in Version 1.9.0: MORE EVERYTHING! This version includes three exciting new power packs and some great FREE stuff that you ve been asking for! This version adds powerful editing features: Don t like a shot in the middle of your video Now you can easily shoot a new one! Use the clip editor to choose the best take for each scene. New copy and paste functions let you copy a scene and paste it to the end of your video. Or paste to the beginning of a brand new video. All these new editing features are FREE so update today! This version lets you import a photo into your video then resize pan and rotate it just the way you want and use it in your video. FREE! There are three power packs to supercharge your videos with nitro burning awesomeness. BFF Best Fantasy Fonts! We created a collection of fourteen beautiful fun quirky swirly fonts to use with your text and titles. Words just can t describe how cool these fonts are but we think you re gonna love em so be sure to check out the demo in the app! Photo Essentials The Overlays have landed! Add some magic to your imported photos with new double exposure and brighten effects and then make them move using any of four animation styles on top of live video. Super Mega Me An awesome new green screen pack that clones resizes flips and fades the foreground subject i.e. YOU . Be careful the normal rules of physics don t apply when you re using these effects and if you wind up on another planet we can t get you back. Hat tip to YouTuber SmashingEpicness for inspiring the Prev Frame effect here! Last but not least: iTunes File Sharing. You can now transfer your Video Star video projects between your iOS device and a computer to back them up and free up space on your device. We added support for iOS 6 iPhone 5 Bluetooth audio and we fixed some bugs! Animated flowers hearts and stars are dancing once again!

You ve been asking and now the most requested feature besides instant fame and recording with Justin comes to Video Star: TITLES! Add a fancy intro do a shout out lay in some lyrics give credit to your friends ask for likes and subscribers ... it s all possible with the new title effects. What kind of titles Check these out: one line multiple lines adjustable layouts slides reveals rotates spins splits zooms morphs all with configurable font size and color! We ve even added a new color effect for those times when you want a title on a solid color background. And for the power users you can now delete more than one previous recording. Sweet! Along the way we ve fixed some bugs YouTube uploads work even better and added a few more dashes of awesome. All excellent and all in this free update. Get it now!

Bolder Color ado the AWESOMEST Power Pack yet! Many video effects are subtle meant to impart feelings of peace and calm like a cup of hot cocoa on a cold winter s day. NOT THESE!!! We found a whole new way to add INTENSITY and WEIRDNESS to your Video Star videos by warping the colors in ways that ways that can only be called psychedelic. Here s what you ll get: RGB Split: creates 3D color offsets along the edges of people and things in the video image. Perfect paired with some mangled dubstep audio. Color Maps: 16 adjustable color distortion effects that will RADICALLY transform your videos. You can dial in just the shift you want or use the dynamic Go version that constantly changed the colors. Truly other worldly! Edge effects: finds edges in your video and creates intense outlines to highlight them. With B W Color and Neon variations. Color Scribble: a new color version of the very popular B W Scribble effect. Black White: what if there were exactly two colors in the world Tint Up: OK this one can actually be kind of subtle. Pushes colors toward bluish reddish yellowish or any other ish. Check out the Bolder Color ado demo video in the app! Also we fixed some bugs! we hateses the bugs

And More Free stuff! New color effects! We ve added amazing new Cartoon Gray and Pastel. New

Pick a color in your scene and have it replaced with colors patterns images ... even your own photos! optimizations for the new iPad new Shrink layout in Crazy Party Effects QuickSnap photos taken in portrait now rotated White balance locked with the AE button minor bug fixes and performance improvements v1.5 We ve been working overtime to bring you the best video tools on a mobile device. First in response to MANY user requests you can now take a quick snapshot of your crazy video effects and blast it to the world via email facebook twitter and the camera roll. We call it Quick Snap ... you ll call it great fun! We ve added AutoExposure lock and AutoFocus lock for iPhone 4 4S . And there are new effects performance improvements and bug fixes. Great stuff and all free in this update. But wait there s more! Our special effects lab has concocted some of the wildest funnest and most amazing video effect Power Packs you ve ever seen. Crazy Party Effects are a must for EVERY video even if you re not at a party. 21 brand new effects. When you are serious about taking your videos to the next level you ll want to get the Split Screen Effects. These let you jump from one part of the screen to the next with continuous action or quick scene and possible costume changes in between. And finally the Advanced AutoStop pack let s you streamline your recording making fast jump cuts and stop motion recordings a breeze. These Power Packs are ready and waiting for you. Just click the lightning bolt button next Video Star s logo and check out the demo videos!
